Property Wars, Season 2, Episode 23.
Title: Lou Makes a Deal.

First aired on July 25, 2013.

Description: The buyers scramble to get to the first house today, but Scott won't have time to inspect it. Lou fills in, but will he be able to tell if it's a winner? Next, Doug and Scott duke it out until a little unexpected interference proves to be a game changer.

Note: web capture.
